{"tid":202362,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先同條女係譚仔食野，條女比人啤","createTime":"2017-04-15T12:26:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T13:54:10.000Z","uid":5190,"like":7,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63d968af0d7612d154e9145d4a22d57e51be0170","tid":202362,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的 頭先同女朋友仔係譚仔食緊野<br />\n<br />\n大家都好肚我 碗野黎到就緊係巴巴聲食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食食下 對面條友無啦啦係到啤鳩我條女 我<br />\n<br />\n即刻問佢「你啤乜撚野呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」佢話我條<br />\n<br />\n女食米線食到啲湯彈撚到佢，我火都黎撚<br />\n<br />\n埋，一巴就打撚左落條女塊臉到，再大聲講<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仆街，你咁大個人有無家教架？屌你老母啲湯彈撚到人呀，講對唔住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n佢即刻喊晒口同對面條友講對唔住<br />\n<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你個臭閪，我今晚就執多你幾濟教撚返好你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n全場靜晒，之後食完就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"227274ed675daef8bd324335e888c20d4aff894f","tid":202362,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"樓主Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b22e93bf046b1d69b556c73451d7e58c294b4e","tid":202362,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以話女依家野 一定要教乖佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e3870286fb0f1372b6d2447d38866dc3f6ac94","tid":202362,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"負評個啲係咪絲打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a442f03c7c358c0d30aa28cce08c9bbc1c5835","tid":202362,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"ab9757565d74f9f76417adbe189eec1f3a594511","tid":202362,"uid":79427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果你條女d米線彈到我 <br />\n我實成條啜入口 <br />\n前前後後出出入入<br />\n先再吞"},{"pid":"49b82b15ff827b5f8db4eb314264db2a3d8430c4","tid":202362,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:48:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你條女d米線彈到我 <br />\n我實成條啜入口 <br />\n前前後後出出入入<br />\n先再吞</blockquote><br />\n米線啲湯呀盲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d519666a77da212b86e7e6acd2c5346bf9cc2f","tid":202362,"uid":15952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你條女d米線彈到我 <br />\n我實成條啜入口 <br />\n前前後後出出入入<br />\n先再吞</blockquote><br />\n但係會望實樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20af54a5730f09f0e331d12444062c239cd57819","tid":202362,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好man"},{"pid":"8133cfffe768b2b170e86237ba6d9839ef7a4ffe","tid":202362,"uid":18535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T13:28:55.000Z","msg":"樓主高汁"},{"pid":"37c4bca7a1976bc62c759ff5e7b4c19368f7ff0a","tid":202362,"uid":101028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T19:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果你條女d米線彈到我 <br />\n我實成條啜入口 <br />\n前前後後出出入入<br />\n先再吞</blockquote><br />\n米線啲湯呀盲閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講如果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=